    <p>Meticulous precision across every document type—from complex manuscript formatting and grant proposals to structured journal rebuttals and technical reports. Every project is refined to meet your exact style guidelines, guaranteed.</p>\n          <div class=\"service-tags-container\">\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">LaTeX</span>\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">MS-Office</span>\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Google Workspace with AI</span>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"service-col\">\n    <div class=\"service-card\">\n      <div class=\"service-card-top\">\n          <div class=\"service-card-header\">\n            <div class=\"service-icon-wrap-1\">💻</div>\n            <h3>Research Coding</h3>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"service-card-bottom\">\n          <p>Spend less time debugging and more time discovering. I use AI-driven workflows to script analysis pipelines and build statistical models that are clean, documented, and ready for publication.</p>\n          <div class=\"service-tags-container\">\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Python / Quarto</span>\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Data Pipelines</span>\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">AI-Automation</span>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"service-col\">\n    <div class=\"service-card\">\n      <div class=\"service-card-top\">\n          <div class=\"service-card-header\">\n            <div class=\"service-icon-wrap\">🎨</div>\n            <h3>Academic Design</h3>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"service-card-bottom\">\n          <p>Turn your raw data into clear visual stories. Whether you need the mathematical precision of LaTeX Beamer, the versatility of PowerPoint, or the creative speed of AI-driven design, I deliver high-quality figures and slides ready for your next defense.</p>\n          <div class=\"service-tags-container\">\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Figures &amp; Charts</span>\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Conference Slides</span>\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Infographics</span>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"service-col\">\n    <div class=\"service-card\">\n      <div class=\"service-card-top\">\n          <div class=\"service-card-header\">\n            <div class=\"service-icon-wrap-1\">⚙️</div>\n            <h3>Workflow &amp; Admin</h3>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"service-card-bottom\">\n          <p>Stop managing logistics and start managing your lab. I organize your digital workspace, handle the friction of scheduling, and implement collaboration tools that keep your projects on track—giving you the headspace to focus on high-impact work.</p>\n          <div class=\"service-tags-container\">\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Calendar Management</span>\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Notion / Obsidian</span>\n            <span class=\"service-tag\">Lab Coordination</span>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<section id=\"webdev\" class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"section-label\">Web Development</div>\n  <h2 class=\"section-title\">Websites That Work as Hard as You Do</h2>\n  <p class=\"section-body\">\n    Stop fighting with outdated university templates and clunky WordPress themes.\n    Whether you're one researcher building a personal presence, a lab recruiting its\n    next cohort, or a department launching its next conference — I build modern,\n    frictionless websites that put the work front and centre.\n  </p>\n  <div class=\"section-divider\"></div>\n\n\n  <div class=\"wd-showcase\">\n    <div class=\"enrollment-badge\">\n      <span class=\"blink-dot\"></span> Live Websites\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"hero-carousel-container\">\n      <div class=\"hero-carousel\" id=\"heroCarousel\">\n\n        <div class=\"hero-carousel-card\">\n          <div class=\"carousel-preview\">\n            <div class=\"mini-browser-bar\">\n              <span class=\"dot red\"></span><span class=\"dot yellow\"></span><span class=\"dot green\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"preview-image-container\">\n              <img src=\"/images/Livesite_2.png\" alt=\"Academic portfolio site\" class=\"carousel-screenshot\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"carousel-info\">\n            <div class=\"carousel-info-text\">\n              <span class=\"carousel-tag tag-portfolio\">Portfolio</span>\n              <h4>Prof. A Chakraborty</h4>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"https://amritachakraborty-bitsh.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"carousel-live-btn\">Live Site ↗</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"hero-carousel-card\">\n          <div class=\"carousel-preview\">\n            <div class=\"mini-browser-bar\">\n              <span class=\"dot red\"></span><span class=\"dot yellow\"></span><span class=\"dot green\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"preview-image-container\">\n              <img src=\"/images/Livesite_1.png\" alt=\"Lab website\" class=\"carousel-screenshot\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"carousel-info\">\n            <div class=\"carousel-info-text\">\n              <span class=\"carousel-tag tag-lab\">Lab &amp; Research</span>\n              <h4>D-cubed lab</h4>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"https://suparnobhattacharyya.github.io/home.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"carousel-live-btn\">Live Site ↗</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"hero-carousel-card\">\n          <div class=\"carousel-preview\">\n            <div class=\"mini-browser-bar\">\n              <span class=\"dot red\"></span><span class=\"dot yellow\"></span><span class=\"dot green\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"preview-image-container\">\n              <img src=\"/images/Livesite_3.png\" alt=\"Conference website\" class=\"carousel-screenshot\">\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"carousel-info\">\n            <div class=\"carousel-info-text\">\n              <span class=\"carousel-tag tag-conference\">Summer School</span>\n              <h4>D2MMS-2026</h4>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"https://people.iitism.ac.in/~d2mms/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"carousel-live-btn\">Live Site ↗</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"carousel-controls\">\n        <button id=\"btn-prev\" class=\"carousel-btn\" aria-label=\"Previous\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left\"></i></button>\n        <div class=\"carousel-dots\" id=\"carouselDots\"></div>\n        <button id=\"btn-next\" class=\"carousel-btn\" aria-label=\"Next\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></button>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n    document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", () => {\n      const carousel = document.getElementById('heroCarousel');\n      const btnPrev = document.getElementById('btn-prev');\n      const btnNext = document.getElementById('btn-next');\n      const dotsWrap = document.getElementById('carouselDots');\n      if (!carousel) return;\n\n      const cards = carousel.querySelectorAll('.hero-carousel-card');\n      cards.forEach((_, i) => {\n        const dot = document.createElement('button');\n        dot.className = 'carousel-dot';\n        dot.setAttribute('aria-label', `Go to project ${i + 1}`);\n        dot.addEventListener('click', () => {\n          carousel.scrollTo({ left: i * carousel.clientWidth, behavior: 'smooth' });\n        });\n        dotsWrap.appendChild(dot);\n      });\n      const dots = dotsWrap.querySelectorAll('.carousel-dot');\n\n      function updateActiveDot() {\n        const index = Math.round(carousel.scrollLeft / carousel.clientWidth);\n        dots.forEach((dot, i) => i === index ? dot.setAttribute('aria-current', 'true') : dot.removeAttribute('aria-current'));\n      }\n      function scrollHero(direction) {\n        carousel.scrollBy({ left: direction * carousel.clientWidth, behavior: 'smooth' });\n      }\n      if (btnPrev) btnPrev.addEventListener('click', () => scrollHero(-1));\n      if (btnNext) btnNext.addEventListener('click', () => scrollHero(1));\n      carousel.addEventListener('scroll', () => requestAnimationFrame(updateActiveDot));\n\n      let autoScroll = setInterval(moveCarousel, 60000);\n      function moveCarousel() {\n        if (carousel.scrollLeft + carousel.clientWidth >= carousel.scrollWidth - 10) {\n          carousel.scrollTo({ left: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });\n        } else { scrollHero(1); }\n      }\n      carousel.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => clearInterval(autoScroll));\n      carousel.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => autoScroll = setInterval(moveCarousel, 60000));\n      updateActiveDot();\n    });\n  </script>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section id=\"tiers\" class=\"content-section\">\n  \n  <h2 class=\"sub-section-title\">The Website We Build </h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"section-divider\"></div>\n\n  <div class=\"tier-grid\">\n\n        <div class=\"tier-card tc-portfolio\" data-num=\"01\">\n      <div class=\"tier-top\">\n        <div class=\"tier-icon\">🧑‍💻</div>\n        <div class=\"tier-name\">Portfolio &amp; Personal Site</div>\n        <div class=\"tier-tagline\">For individual researchers &amp; developers</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tier-body\">\n        <p class=\"tier-desc\">\n          Your first impression online should be as sharp as your CV.\n          A sleek, fast personal site that puts your publications, projects,\n          and credentials front and centre.\n        </p>\n        <ul class=\"tier-features\">\n          <li>Publications, CV &amp; project showcase</li>\n          <li>Interactive data &amp; tool integration</li>\n          <li>Free hosting via GitHub Pages (zero ongoing server costs)</li>\n          <li>Built with quality</li>\n        </ul>\n        <a href=\"/contact.qmd\" class=\"tier-cta\">Get Your Site →</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tier-card tc-lab\" data-num=\"02\">\n      <div class=\"tier-top\">\n        <div class=\"tier-icon\">🔬</div>\n        <div class=\"tier-name\">Lab &amp; Research Group</div>\n        <div class=\"tier-tagline\">For PIs, research groups &amp; core facilities</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tier-body\">\n        <p class=\"tier-desc\">\n          Your lab is a team, a body of work, and a pipeline of talent you're\n          trying to attract. A multi-page site showcasing your group's people,\n          publications, and ongoing projects.\n        </p>\n        <ul class=\"tier-features\">\n          <li>Team, alumni &amp; collaborator pages</li>\n          <li>\"Join us\" recruiting page for students &amp; postdocs</li>\n          <li>Grant &amp; funding acknowledgment blocks</li>\n          <li>Free hosting via GitHub Pages (zero ongoing server costs)</li>\n        </ul>\n        <a href=\"/contact.qmd\" class=\"tier-cta\">Build My Lab's Website →</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tier-card tc-conference\" data-num=\"03\">\n      <div class=\"tier-top\">\n        <div class=\"tier-icon\">🎙️</div>\n        <div class=\"tier-name\">Conference &amp; Event Site</div>\n        <div class=\"tier-tagline\">For departments &amp; institutions hosting an event</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tier-body\">\n        <p class=\"tier-desc\">\n          A dedicated hub attendees actually use — schedule, speakers, and\n          submissions in one place, so your organizing committee stops\n          fielding the same emails on repeat.\n        </p>\n        <ul class=\"tier-features\">\n          <li>Schedule &amp; speaker agenda</li>\n          <li>Abstract / paper submission portal</li>\n          <li>Registration &amp; sponsor showcase</li>\n          <li>Built to handle a traffic spike on launch day</li>\n        </ul>\n        <a href=\"/contact.qmd\" class=\"tier-cta\">Build My Conference Site →</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wd-cta content-section\">\n  <h2>One Platform, Whichever You Need</h2>\n  <p>\n    Async support to lift the everyday demands of academic life, or a website built to put\n    your work front and centre — I keep a small client roster so every project gets real\n    attention. Tell me which one fits, and I'll tell you exactly what it takes to get there.\n  </p>\n  <div class=\"wd-cta-actions\">\n    <a href=\"/contact.qmd\" class=\"btn-primary-wd\">Let's Get Started →</a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n```\n\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":"auto","echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":t